    "date": "2020-07-13T16:57:58Z",
    "text": "Emergency Housing Assistance for Older Adults Act of 2020\n\nThis bill authorizes additional assistance for supportive housing for the elderly.\n\nAmong other things, the bill authorizes additional rental assistance for low-income elderly persons and additional grants to certain federally assisted housing projects to provide service coordinators to prevent, prepare for, or respond to the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) public health emergency."
